title: Sidewall
description: Toile de Jouy paper. Provincial scenes of horsemen hunting boars and stags. A small village is shown, another group shows these men gathered about a keg of wine or beer. Also shown are a huntsman, surrounded by hounds, sounding his horn and a rider inquiring his way from a farmer; printed in pinkish-red on light beige, plaid ground.
name: Sidewall
